Detailed Description

template<class T>
class gaia::base::HashSet< T >

Implements hashset data structure and operation methods.

Hashset makes use of HashMap to realize its functions.

See also:
HashMap
 // Create a hashset
 HashSet<int> hsInt;

 // Add datum into this hashset
 if (hsInt.size() == 0) {
        for (size_t i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
            hsInt.add(i);
        }
 }
 
 // Remove one data out of hashset
 hsInt.remove(10);
 
 // Clear all datum.
 hsInt.clear();
